 *
 * @fields_start
 *
 * group:logo => 品牌标识设置
 * logo.display => 显示品牌标识:select:yes|yes,no
 * logo.text => 品牌旁文本:text:Indian Rummy Voltage
 * logo.subline => 品牌副标题:text:
 * logo.url => 品牌标识地址:textarea:|默认使用本地logo-icon-128.avif
 * logo.width => 品牌标识宽度:responsive:70/70|px
 * logo.height => 品牌标识高度:responsive:|px[可选，默认使用width值]
 *
 * group:navigation => 导航设置
